Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:06.01,kaitou,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}体育祭结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一个沃斯套餐对吧？谢谢您的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一份沃斯套餐——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有这个收银台排这么长的队？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边的那个不是没有什么人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  没什么人算我走运了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么在生气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容是免费的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我说我要笑容～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被  被拉到里面去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊！拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起！请稍候片刻！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉  拉拉同学  不可以这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  一条…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想办法搞定她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下！快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  拉拉最近相当的暴躁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育祭上被一条打败的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在耿耿于怀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不吃要凉了  伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…也许会回国去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉  这是惯例的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖剩下的汉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你明天接待客人的时候可以再多笑一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要输给一条…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…打起精神来  拉拉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都有做不来的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果拉拉同学能笑一笑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定会很可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康介？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点回去的话多基比隆就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙好高！那么你就是多基比隆里的邪恶女王吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！康介！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒你！放马过来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  拉拉同学  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  放开我！放开我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:07:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒邪恶女王！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adios（再见）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是独自一人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  来做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要昨天那样的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一条救救我——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再这样啦！拉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今鸟同学  你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳头的力量和昨天不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不用再来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下！快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喧嚣原始人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(496,397)\3c&H000000\fad(500,500)}旁白   {\fs33}小林  尽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间是一万年之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原始时代的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不清是土器时代还是石器时代的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  人类确实生存着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样用绳子转一圈  就会出现纹理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱哦  一定会流行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云真聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把图画在树叶上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想出来的  叫做动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  真有趣！真有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说出来啊  越说越饿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  今年山产的收成不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会饿死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟糕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花  花井他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞口水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然平时觉得他是个吵吵闹闹总惹麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰嘎啦轰嘎  哈莱诺帮嘎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！他还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说他死了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫  烫  烫死了——!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  果然还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水！快拿水来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊  花井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了寻找食物进了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了一棵果树  爬树摘果子的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一头巨大无比的猛犸象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的猛犸象…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Task（巨大恶魔）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片矢神森林中很久前就传说着的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成很麻烦的事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Task…那个恶魔出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  看起来没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  村里所有人都会饿死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以女王身份下令！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召开对策会议！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  今天画的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵子在山里发现的这种黑色的石头很硬很好用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里的网点有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网点是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满  我爱你  Baby！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先成为问题的是它的皮肤！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太硬了  我们的石头武器对它没有用！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆我们下决心放弃这块土地如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  跟着我花井走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我深爱着这里的山川河流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找出更加坚硬的石头来就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…可是没有那么坚硬的石头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想吃冻糕啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冻糕是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有吃饭所以饿得动不了了吗！真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…肚子饿了…播磨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  稍微打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  播磨  你这家伙怎么跑到村子里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:23.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被赶走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为太粗暴而且又傻  被女王下令驱逐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！请听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所找到的这个黑色石头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比现在发现的所有石头都要坚硬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用这种石头制作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该连Devil Task也可以战胜！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨那家伙在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头能有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是石头武器能够打败Devil Task的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用这么辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要用那个去烤番薯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤番薯是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也许播磨说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！预言家大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用这种黑色石头来强化武器的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为有尝试的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就试试看吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦  播磨！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  没有什么了不得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  要在这里显出我的威风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小满爱上我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爸  你要努力的去打猎农晚餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题！包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着吧  我的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多为了村子拼上性命的年轻人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是都是因为我的美貌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！没有什么可怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心跟着我花井前进吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说  你的动画新作做好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My family…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲锋——！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用黑色石头做成的武器来战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行吗？所以我说了要跟着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！不要放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！插进Devil Task那坚硬的皮肤里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊！播磨！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！这样小满的心就是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一·条！就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔！勇者拉拉和一·条成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！所有人一起去干掉它！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以过冬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是多亏了拉拉和一·条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  大家一起赞扬这两位勇者吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好！你们两个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一·条！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我只是个粗暴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小满已经吃饱了  这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小满！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力呢  播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这是播磨的份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小满…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有鼻子吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份感动一定要记录下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画得真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要齐心协力  什么都可以做得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因为我们是同伴吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得转世重生的话大家能够做同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是有种感觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块石板是原始时代留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为微笑的维纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…感觉好像姐姐啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.88,kaitou2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}漫画新人奖的截稿日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  我一定要做到！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹  帮我把那里的云形尺拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为打雷吓了一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没关系  我来拣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢  谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  不客气…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停  停电了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜡烛蜡烛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  偏偏在这个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼…虽说是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过碰到女孩子的手真令人心跳加快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  如果我碰到天满的手大概会死掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真安静呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要听广播？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电的时候大家都吓了一跳吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我DJ YOSHIMO可是一点都不怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个时候和女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人单独在房间里亲热是最适合不过的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在就由我YOSHIMO来传授钓女孩子的秘技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家仔细…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是安静的时候比较适合工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你想听刚才的广播？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  让你来帮我真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:10.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  因为我也想快点看到播磨同学完成了的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以就这样不动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…原来光线是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  漫画里有主人公和女主角在洞窟里烤火的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用想象的怎么也想不出来是什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看到刚才的妹妹就把握住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  顺带把这个场面的台词读一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.04,0:21:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能更好地掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「终于成了在无人岛上两人独处的情况了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个！就是这个感觉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…很有参考价值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹你是演技派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么继续往下读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好和我独处的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  好…很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.48,0:22:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  下一句台词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的！放心吧！我会一直保护你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？播  播磨同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接  接着往下读台词就可以了吧  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这句台词…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜…喜…喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗！我也爱着你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好了！我会让你幸福的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个  播磨同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们两个来构筑一个温暖幸福的家庭吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小满…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然…不说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.97,0:23:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是惹他生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.33,0:23:10.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（好  好可爱…小满…）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.01,0:23:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉啊  一不留神就陷进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.28,0:23:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  继续画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.43,0:23:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.04,0:23:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  讨厌男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是喜欢男人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.35,0:25:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到文化祭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.38,0:25:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上因为不知道应该办咖啡厅还是话剧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.56,0:25:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这样的事还有那样的事来决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.38,0:25:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂  这个上次我也说过！
